section.animate-in.space-y-4
	h1.text-5xl.font-bold.tracking-tight.leading-none
		span.gradient-text Examples
	p.text-lg.text-neutral-600.max-w-prose.leading-relaxed
		| The same apps written two ways. Same UI, same behavior — different conventions.

section.animate-in-delayed.pt-12.space-y-3
	.grid.gap-3(class="sm:grid-cols-2")
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/norns")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Norns
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .n
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed Pug + CoffeeScript, the
				code .n
				| extension. Concise.
		a.card-interactive(href="/examples/svelte")
			.flex.items-start.justify-between.gap-3.mb-2
				h2.font-semibold.text-lg Vanilla Svelte
				span.text-xs.text-neutral-400.font-mono.shrink-0.mt-1 .svelte
			p.text-sm.text-neutral-600.leading-relaxed HTML + TypeScript, the
				code .svelte
				| extension. Default.
